PERSPECTIVE: We've gone stir crazy at home, and hate wearing a mask. We have Netflix, Grubhub, our pets, and wine. Still a huge adjustment. This is Anne Frank. She and 7 others hid in a 450 sq.ft. attic for 761 days. They were quiet, to remain undiscovered, so as to stay alive. https://t.co/uNXqSvgN3r
